//		 * Returns the duration of the fragment identified thorugh the provided url.
//		 * 
//		 * @langversion 3.0
//		 * @playerversion Flash 10
//		 * @playerversion AIR 1.5
//		 * @productversion OSMF 1.0
//		 */
